snippet.title: Seasons
snippet.description:
My channel is more of an interactive diary of sorts.. my real love is backyard gardening.. However, due to my growing season being so short you may see - DIY projects, Bargain shopping, Cooking, Crafting, Subscription Box openings.. and even some Drama. you just never know..

I appreciated each of you .. I really enjoy interacting with all of you.. I hope you join me on my Journey of my 4 Seasons..

         *** A SEASON FOR EVERYTHING***
"Everything on earth has its own time and its own SEASON
There is a time for birth and death, planting and reaping,
For killing and healing, destroying and building,
For crying and laughing, weeping and dancing,
For throwing stones and gathering stones,  embracing and parting.
There is a time for finding and losing, keeping and giving,
For tearing and sewing, listening and speaking.
There is also a time
for love and hate, for war and peace. Ecclesiastes 3:1-8

I may be reached at My4Seasons01@gmail.com

Please LIKE & SUBSCRIBE.. 

"
